tool_description: An API to check if a YouTube video is embeddable, not age restricted, removed or blocked in all countries. This API can help website admins to know which YouTube videos are no longer available on their websites.
name: YouTube Embeding Videos Checker
title: YouTube Embeding Videos Checker

api_list.name: /api/YouTube
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://youtube-embeding-videos-checker.p.rapidapi.com/api/YouTube"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "youtube-embeding-videos-checker.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
